  <brief_title>Relationship Between Microcirculatory Flow Alterations and Tissue Metabolism</brief_title>
  <official_title>Correlation Between Microcirculatory Flow and Rectal Anaerobe Cellular CO2 Production in Patients After Cardiac Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
